dez</span> </span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Malegra</span> <span class="hps">DXT </span></span><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">hors de la port&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps">des enfants</span> <span class="hps">et loin des animaux</span><span>.</span></span></p><p><strong><span lang="fr">INFORMATION ADDITIVE:</span></strong></p><p>Les ingr&eacute;dients actifs: Sildenafil et Duloxetine</p><p><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Les effets de</span><span class="hps alt-edited"> ce m&eacute;dicament</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">durent jusqu'&agrave;</span> <span class="hps">4 heures.</span><br /><br /> <span class="hps">Malegra</span> <span class="hps">DXT</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ne doit pas &ecirc;tre consomm&eacute;e</span> <span class="hps">sur une base</span> <span class="hps">quotidienne</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">car elle peut faire</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">l'accoutumance</span>. <span class="hps">Ainsi, ce</span> <span class="hps">type de consommation</span> <span class="hps">peut</span> <span class="hps">mener &agrave; la d&eacute;pendance</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">de ce m&eacute;dicament</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">&agrave; la personne</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">et mettre en &eacute;vidence</span> <span class="hps">les effets secondaires</span> <span class="hps alt-edited">ind&eacute;sirables</span> <span class="hps">sur la personne</span><span>.</span><br /><br /> <span class="hps">En</span> <span class="hps">cas de surdosage</span><span class="alt-edited">, contactez imm&eacute;diatement avec</span> <span class="hps">le centre</span> <span class="hps">antipoison ou la salle</span> <span class="hps">d'urgence.</span></span></p><p><strong>RENSEIGNEMENTS DE S&Eacute;CURIT&Eacute;</strong></p><p><strong><span id="result_box" lang="fr"><span class="hps">Ne prenez pas </span></span>Malegra DXT si:</strong></p><ul><li><span id="result_box" la